Action: to update the multiple records - click on ModifyStatus button.- when you providing the status on popup.

defaine behavior for zr_dbt_trav alias R_DBT_TRAV
persistent table ZDBT_TRAV
extensible
draft table ZDBT_TRAV_D
etag master LastchangedAt
lock master total etag LastchangedAt
authotization master( global )
{

  field ( mandatory : create )
    TravelID;

  field (readonly )
    Lastchengedat;

  field( readonly : update )
   TravelID;

  create:
  update;
  delete;

  draft action  Activate optimized;
  draft action Discard;
  draft action Edit;
  draft action Resume;
  draft determine action Prepare;
  action UpdateStatus parameter zstatus_str  --> ctrl + 1 --> create structure

  mapping for zdbt_trav corresponding extensible 
  { 
    TravelID = TRAVEL_ID;
    Description = DESCRIPTION;
    status = STATUS;
    Lastchangedat = LASTCHANGEDAT;
    CreatedBy = CREATEDBY;
    Lastchangedby = LASTCHANGEDBY;

  }
  }

behavior implementation class:
_____________________________

class lhc_zr_dbt_trav definition inheriting from cl_abap_behavior_handler.
private section.
  methods : get_global_authentications for global authorization
            importing request requested_authorizations for r_dbt_Trav
            result result,

            updatestatus for modify
                importing keys for action R_DBT_TRAV~UpdateStatus .
endclass.
class lhc_zr_dbt_trav implementation.
  method get_global_authentications.
  endmethod.

  method updatestatus.
    modify entities of zr_dbt_trav in local mode entity r_dbt_trav
    update fields ( Status )
    with value #( for key in keys ( %key-TravelId = Key-TravelId
                                    status = key-%param-status ) ) 
    reported data( lt_reported )
    failed data( lt_failed ).
  endmethod.
endclass.

Output:
Selected 2 records from output --> clikc on modify status --> popup appears -- with status - T( input value ) -- 
clikc on modifystatus button --> it will update the status 'T" to selected records. 
Travel status updated 'T' with multiple records.

Scenario:
_________________
- after updation - currently our travel status is 'T'- when i am trying to update - to 'R', -- clikc on modify status -->
immediately the result after updation od db will not return immediately to the UI, --> it will return when click on "GO' button.
Once click on GO button- 'R" update...

but these functionality we have to overwrite -- after clicking on ModifyStatus button --> 
data should be update and immediately visible to the user at ui level ( Not required to click the GO button)

Solution:
_________
- need to add the result paramenter in action.- means whetever updated values to the return- immediately.

action UpdateStatus parameter zstatus_Str  result[1] $self;
here:
$self - it represents the current entity. means which entity return the results.

